##DISPLAYNAME Shutdown All
##DESCRIPTION Shuts down all XVMs in the system

assume launch-all has run

// stop the send driver
stop the fraudanalyzer-send-driver app in the fraudanalyzer-send-driver xvm

// shutdown the processor cluster
stop the fraudanalyzer app in the fraudanalyzer-2 xvm
stop the fraudanalyzer app in the fraudanalyzer-1 xvm

// stop the receive driver
stop the fraudanalyzer-receive-driver app in the fraudanalyzer-receive-driver xvm

shutdown
